1. d4 Nf6 2. Bg5 {(Trompovsky’s move)} c6 3. e3 $4 {(overlooking Black’s 
threat of check)} Qa5+ {(and winning the Bishop after... Qxg5 (Djordjevic - 
Kovacevic, Bela Crka 1984 This is a common theme of checking with the Queen, 
then sliding horizontally to win a piece.))} *

